{"tid":1295362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣策略】無論今後前線做左D咩，都要堅持話佢地係和平嘅","createTime":"2019-07-08T03:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T06:33:34.000Z","uid":270871,"like":122,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ab69b7a690ad102a0a9503f27aff12b619dadaaf","tid":1295362,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:58:25.000Z","msg":"好多人同人解釋佔領立法會嗰時<br />\n都會解釋前因後果、政府制度暴力之類，講點解要行動升級<br />\n咁樣係好，但就忽略左仲有個重點就係：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">暴力嘅定義真係冇得拗咩？</span><br />\n<br />\n經常被香港視為勇武抗爭典範嘅烏克蘭其實喺國際社會眼中都係和平示威黎<br />\n只要將「和平示威」同「內戰」比較咁就好易拗<br />\n「爆玻璃又冇傷人有咩暴力？」「又唔係揸槍駁火有咩暴力？」「自衛咋有咩暴力？」「只針對政府咋有咩暴力？」等等<br />\n即使唔可以即時說服到對方覺得唔暴力，都可以挑戰到佢固有觀念<br />\n<br />\n正如以前行出馬路都俾人屌到飛起，宜家佔路變最低消費<br />\n以前掟野會俾人鬧暴徒，宜家變得不值一提<br />\n以前撞立法會導致內訌割蓆，宜家大家齊聲支持<br />\n所以我地要<span style=\"color: red;\">不斷擴闊對和平嘅想像</span>，咁樣先方便前線做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4acfd78ca62c8f9335f2afb3c4324d9f1770c494","tid":1295362,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:59:40.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"38f8250ea740f7255feeb24d63ee4d0b21f8033c","tid":1295362,"uid":255105,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:02:12.000Z","msg":"應該盡力推廣和理優概念，取代過時既和理非。和理優易入口好多。"},{"pid":"466e6232ed86c0263f76fb899f7a61b096223655","tid":1295362,"uid":270871,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:03:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZAo1Hr7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZAo1Hr7.gif&h=c659fd7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86f3d8190a6036ef4a8aa4f02a87608cb9edd90b","tid":1295362,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:05:44.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"702ef7cfc90b3b698fab03a98719bd9eca9d5379","tid":1295362,"uid":140431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:06:54.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f21c637280a24c91ee41f2704a209c7a9a937eb4","tid":1295362,"uid":213747,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:07:06.000Z","msg":"啲狗拎埋槍出黎射都話自己唔係暴力<br />\n示威者頂多都係推鐵馬爆玻璃 真係邊忽暴力"},{"pid":"703db4c2bcb4bf1789a40efc4873a44a88fa21af","tid":1295362,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:08:24.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"8a86978b7b4265e2b3b21054ee48d29af252612a","tid":1295362,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:10:12.000Z","msg":"我唔解鎖"},{"pid":"73a03817969b910778ce3e301968e5a2f45b0d42","tid":1295362,"uid":267621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f21c637280a24c91ee41f2704a209c7a9a937eb4","tid":1295362,"uid":213747,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:07:06.000Z","msg":"啲狗拎埋槍出黎射都話自己唔係暴力<br />\n示威者頂多都係推鐵馬爆玻璃 真係邊忽暴力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:10:27.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"a584073c10d06df3b5d170ef6a02d5bea4e59c96","tid":1295362,"uid":209609,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:12:12.000Z","msg":"不如直接話71係和平衝立會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b1184f760490d3ef43a502e5f2f91525d1f867","tid":1295362,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:12:23.000Z","msg":"我要見律師"},{"pid":"48e3a516ac08ad10c5b25373e4be2e05c04154b4","tid":1295362,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:14:44.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"a524e0398c98799e62e313c2768586efa5219fe8","tid":1295362,"uid":67294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:16:32.000Z","msg":"點解要呢個時候發表啲咁既言論<br />\n事實上琴日77旺角係和平，連鐵馬都無<br />\n<br />\n你咁講有啲暗示緊琴日示威者有暴力衝擊，希望你澄清下"},{"pid":"44676b59beaecf27e26a8453c752ded99140e194","tid":1295362,"uid":270871,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a524e0398c98799e62e313c2768586efa5219fe8","tid":1295362